  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the health effects of benzene exposure in workers
      in Shanghai, China.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the dose-response relationship between benzene
      exposure and blood diseases in Shanghai workers and to characterize genetic polymorphisms
      that are associated with increased risk of developing benzene hematotoxicity.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
